HEADWORD: Upsun
<hw>Up"sun`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld>
<def>The time during which the sun is up, or above the horizon; the time
between sunrise and sunset.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

